title: Production of Rye in Canada 2020
summary: The graph shows the Production of Rye Canada ( in Tonnes ) in Canada the year 2020 .
Production is very different over the year .
While a significant decline in Production can be observed from January to February , Production continues to rise until April , reaching its annual maximum of more than 42000 Tonnes .
gold: The production of rye in Canada measured in tonnes , for each month of the year 2020 . The production is the highest in August and the lowest in July . .
